**LIX calculator used:** https://www.skriva.se/skriva-klart/lixtal.aspx

**Total number of characters excluding spaces:** 651
**Total number of words:** 128
**Total number of sentences:** 16

**LIX score calculation:**
```
LIX = (characters / words) + (100 * sentences / words)
```
```
LIX = (651 / 128) + (100 * 16 / 128)
```
```
LIX = 5.12 + 12.5
```
```
LIX = 17.62
```

**Result:**
LIX=17.62